    • opacity

      @NotNull @Contract(pure=true) public static @NotNull org.jsfml.graphics.Color opacity​(@NotNull @NotNull org.jsfml.graphics.Color color, float opacity)
      Returns the color specified in the first parameter with the specified alpha (opacity) value
      Parameters:
      color - a color
      opacity - the color's opacity value ranging between 0.0f (fully transparent) and 1.0f (fully opaque)
      Returns:
      the specified color with the specified opacity
